{"actor":"Rohit Garud","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-05T21:23:21Z","event_type":"claimed","id":45,"issue_id":"agent-arsenal-s7g","new_value":"{\"assignee\":\"Rohit Garud\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"agent-arsenal-s7g\",\"title\":\"FEAT: Add --verbose/-v flag for detailed execution output\",\"description\":\"Agents need verbose output for debugging and logging.\\n\\nExpected behavior:\\n- arsenal --verbose common uuid  # Show execution details\\n- Output: Executing handler: uuid.handle_uuid\\n-         Args: {'version': 4, 'count': 1}\\n-         Result: 0392dc98-b367-4aa2-879f-0bd44935413b\\n\\nThis helps agents:\\n1. Debug command execution\\n2. Log detailed traces\\n3. Understand failures\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":2,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"rohit.garuda1992@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-05T04:45:06Z\",\"created_by\":\"Rohit Garud\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-05T04:45:06Z\"}"}
